sentences.english: This is a preview, not the V1 release.
sentences.chinese: 這依舊是一個預覽版，並非V1版。

sentences.english: This article provides a quick-reference guide for the new functionality offered in the technical preview.
sentences.chinese: 本文提供了技術預覽版新功能的快速參考指南。

sentences.english: Now everything above the bar is a summary, or preview, of the article.
sentences.chinese: 現在欄上的內容只有一個文章摘要，或預覽。

sentences.english: For first time, Toolbag a simple tool that uses the Marmoset game engine and include a real time model viewer.
sentences.chinese: 我是第一次使用猴子游戲引擎，包括實時模型的預覽。

sentences.english: A sliding sidebar on the left-hand side displays a page switcher with thumbnail previews.
sentences.chinese: 左邊欄的滑動條還可以顯示帶預覽圖的分頁切換。

sentences.english: The property is available for preview daily from 1 to 4 pm and by appointment.
sentences.chinese: 每日下午1點到4點可入宅預覽，請提前預約。

sentences.english: Offering a print-preview for PDF files.
The same one can be reused for both preview and publishing.
sentences.chinese: 同一個表示模板可在預覽和發佈時重複使用。

sentences.english: You will be able to see a preview of the image that you upload.
sentences.chinese: 您將看到您上傳圖片的預覽圖。

sentences.english: For a new application, the preview shows zero documents in the database.
sentences.chinese: 對於新應用程序，預覽顯示數據庫中有零個文檔。

sentences.english: The report can be previewed with no data or limited data.
sentences.chinese: 報表可以在無數據或限制數據情況下預覽。

sentences.english: Finally, two limitations and future research directions on theories of RJP are discussed.
sentences.chinese: 指出現實工作預覽研究存在的問題和今後的研究方向。

sentences.english: However, there will be some differences between the previewed version and the final version.
sentences.chinese: 然而，預覽版本和最後版本之間存在一些不同。

sentences.english: Developers can find out more about the upcoming features by accessing the early access program, which periodically provides a sneak peak of what's coming next.
sentences.chinese: 開發者可以訪問早期預覽版以瞭解即將到來的新特性。

sentences.english: Museum guests preview the "Summer of China" series.
sentences.chinese: 博物館的賓客在預覽“中國夏日”系列展。

sentences.english: You can run a preview at any time without any impact to the system.
sentences.chinese: 您可以在任何時候運行預覽，這不會對系統造成影響。
